                  <summary><p>The <title xml:lang="ta">Arunaikiripurāṇam</title>, that is, the <title xml:lang="ta">Aruṇācalapurāṇam</title>, which is the <emph rend="italic" xml:lang="ta">talapurāṇam</emph> of <placeName xml:lang="ta">Tiruvaṇṇāmalai</placeName>. Text complete (577 or 587 stanzas) and commentary.</p>
